who is going to steal this money but he has a constraints/rule that he cannot steal/rob two adjacent houses. Find the maximum 
money he can rob.


TEST CASE 1:
2
5 10
2 12

OUTPUT:
30
12

TEST CASE 2:
3
6 12
1 10
8 5

OUTPUT:
36
10
20
